{"blogid": "121278067", "writerAge": "码龄8年", "writerBlogNum": "23", "writerCollect": "170", "writerComment": "17", "writerFan": "19", "writerGrade": "3级", "writerIntegral": "470", "writerName": "秃头菜鸟", "writerProfileAdress": "..\\..\\static\\writer_image\\profile_121278067.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "129622", "writerRankWeekly": "122788", "writerThumb": "37", "writerVisitNum": "48401", "blog_read_count": "9055", "blog_time": "于 2021-11-11 23:03:25 发布", "blog_title": "vscode配置运行php项目完整版", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"../../static/bootstrap/css/csdnstyle.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"markdown_views prism-github-gist\" id=\"content_views\">\n<svg style=\"display: none;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M5,0 0,2.5 5,5z\" id=\"raphael-marker-block\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></path>\n</svg>\n<h1><a id=\"PHP_0\"></a>第一步，下载PHP</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.php.net/\">php官网地址</a><br/> windows 下载直接解压即可<br/> liunx请自行csdn搜索教程</p>\n<h1><a id=\"code_6\"></a>第二步，下载code插件</h1>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\0d4ef7a23e86429a861f5fab0460c91d.png\"/></p>\n<h2><a id=\"1_PHP_Debug_10\"></a>1. PHP Debug</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>控制台debug<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\0c4c86af9b6a474aab37211074bc38b4.png\"/></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3><a id=\"_16\"></a>配置</h3>\n<p>路径为PHP解压后的运行文件路径，代码放配置的根节点</p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-json\"><span class=\"token string\">\"php.validate.executablePath\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"D:/Program Files/php/php.exe\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">\"php.debug.executablePath\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"D:/Program Files/php/php.exe\"</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2><a id=\"2_PHP_Intelephense_25\"></a>2. PHP Intelephense</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>强大的php代码提示器</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\bfc69705476d47078123802ad1a01048.png\"/><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\67f5ed2e212f4cdca80663990ce861cf.png\"/></p>\n<h2><a id=\"3_PHP_server_32\"></a>3. PHP server</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>运行PHP服务器<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\9c838917ccc446848b7c82cdc852ea16.png\"/></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3><a id=\"_38\"></a>配置</h3>\n<p>同样放配置在settings.json文件的根节点</p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-objectivec\"> <span class=\"token string\">\"phpserver.phpPath\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"D:/Program Files/php/php.exe\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token comment\">//PHP运行文件</span>\n <span class=\"token string\">\"phpserver.browser\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"C:\\\\Program Files\\\\Google\\\\Chrome\\\\Application\\\\chrome.exe\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token comment\">//浏览器</span>\n <span class=\"token string\">\"phpserver.phpConfigPath\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"D:/Program Files/php/php.ini\"</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//配置文件</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h1><a id=\"phpini_47\"></a>第三步，配置php.ini</h1>\n<p>将解压后的<strong>D:/Program Files/php/ext</strong>目录复制到c盘的<strong>C:\\php\\ext</strong><br/> 然后在解压的php目录下新建一个<strong>php.ini</strong>配置文件<br/> 如果直接将php解压在c盘的可以忽略此操作</p>\n<h2><a id=\"phpini_52\"></a>php.ini配置</h2>\n<p>需要使用的驱动写入即可，对应ext目录内容</p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-objectivec\">extension<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>php_mysqli<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dll\nextension<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>php_pdo_mysql<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dll\nextension<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>php_pdo_sqlite<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dll\n</code></pre>\n<p>PHPserver运行代码查看配置文件是否生效</p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-php\"><span class=\"token delimiter important\">&lt;?php</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">phpinfo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\5774d12c9eef4bc6b9ccd65d92ad4431.png\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\19cb5fefd1b24d2a840a3863481cf5f7.png\"/></p>\n</div>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/editerView/markdown_views-22a2fefd3b.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/style-4f8fbf9108.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n</div>", "first_tag": "PHP", "cpp": 0, "csharp": 0, "python": 0, "javascript": 0, "java": 0, "sql": 1, "php": 1, "time": "2021-11-11 23:03:25", "summary": "第一步，下载官网地址下载直接解压即可请自行搜索教程第二步，下载插件控制台在这里插入图片描述配置路径为解压后的运行文件路径，代码放配置的根节点强大的代码提示器在这里插入图片描述在这里插入图片描述运行服务"}